# Manqoba Privacy Policy

**Last updated: 19 February 2026**

Manqoba (“we”, “our”, “the app”) provides educational tools and services for students. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

## Information We Collect
- Name  
- Email address  
- Profile picture  
- Authentication UID  
- App usage data  
- School and subscription information (if applicable)

## How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
- Authenticate your account  
- Personalize your learning experience  
- Sync your progress across devices  
- Improve app performance and features  

## How We Store Your Information
Your data is stored using:
- Firebase Authentication  
- Firebase Firestore  
- Firebase Cloud Storage  

We do not sell your data.

## Account Deletion
You may delete your account inside the app.  
This will remove your authentication profile and associated Firestore data.

## Contact Us
If you have questions, contact us at: **arthur.rusike@gmail.com**
